actually make sense.

03:27.875 --> 03:31.020
Anyway, she had a very difficult

03:31.044 --> 03:33.447
relationship with her mother,

03:35.749 --> 03:40.388
who only responded positively
when Julie behaved perfectly,

03:41.955 --> 03:44.668
so Julie never had
any difficulties

03:44.692 --> 03:47.795
with eating or
sleeping or teething,

03:48.862 --> 03:49.997
potty training,

03:53.033 --> 03:54.478
walking or talking.

03:54.502 --> 03:56.846
She was like an automaton.

03:56.870 --> 04:00.808
But she felt that her true
self was being murdered.

04:02.075 --> 04:05.522
"I wasn't mothered,
I was smothered."

04:05.546 --> 04:07.591
"She wasn't a mother,
she was killing me,"

04:07.615 --> 04:10.560
"she was cutting out my tongue."

04:10.584 --> 04:11.885
Because her mother

04:14.555 --> 04:17.301
didn't let her develop,
to become independent,

04:17.325 --> 04:21.394
Julie saw her as a
destructive black sun

04:22.596 --> 04:24.365
blocking out all life.

04:27.868 --> 04:28.936
- Freak!

04:30.504 --> 04:32.015
- Give me the knife.

04:32.039 --> 04:33.450
Put it down.

04:33.474 --> 04:35.752
Raymond, put it down.

04:35.776 --> 04:36.986
Raymond put it,

04:37.010 --> 04:38.512
