04:53.827 --> 04:55.672
You alright?

04:55.696 --> 04:58.375
Yeah.

04:58.399 --> 04:59.676
Shall we?

04:59.700 --> 05:02.546
Come on, good man, let's go.

05:02.570 --> 05:03.570
That's it.

05:05.806 --> 05:09.377
