which they can retreat to.

05:25.526 --> 05:27.604
You have your own private space

05:27.628 --> 05:29.406
that you can get away?

05:29.430 --> 05:33.810
Everyone does, everyone
here has their own space.

05:33.834 --> 05:35.078
Mm, that's nice.

05:35.102 --> 05:37.481
I think that's important,

05:37.505 --> 05:40.850
to give that sense of security.

05:40.874 --> 05:43.644
We're very much one
community, one,

05:45.078 --> 05:47.924
one group of people
living together

05:47.948 --> 05:49.049
as best we can.

05:50.718 --> 05:52.529
But sometimes you need to,

05:52.553 --> 05:55.465
you need to be able
to be by yourself.

05:55.489 --> 05:57.967
I think that's important.

05:57.991 --> 05:59.869
