wash my hands of him,

06:32.575 --> 06:34.538
which I won't do.

06:34.562 --> 06:36.706
What's wrong with him?

06:36.730 --> 06:37.730
Ask him.

06:44.972 --> 06:47.651
There are many
people like Raymond

06:47.675 --> 06:49.686
claiming to be the messiah

06:49.710 --> 06:54.448
and they are incarcerated,
electrocuted,

06:55.048 --> 06:59.028
drugged, restrained,
imprisoned against their will.

06:59.052 --> 07:01.765
Why was he in prison?

07:01.789 --> 07:03.229
Nah, it's not prison
it's a hospital.

07:03.253 --> 07:04.568
Oh.

07:04.592 --> 07:07.136
It's meant to be a
cure not a punishment.

07:07.160 --> 07:08.529
I had no idea.

07:10.030 --> 07:12.809
Is it true you don't
prescribe any drugs?

07:12.833 --> 07:16.513
No tranquilizers, no, no
sedatives of any kind

07:16.537 --> 07:18.515
