07:18.539 --> 07:19.983
And her?

07:20.007 --> 07:21.207
She does have a name you know.

07:23.010 --> 07:24.010
Maria?

07:25.946 --> 07:28.482
Maria, do you want to come
talk to our friend here?

07:33.687 --> 07:35.956
