07:42.663 --> 07:45.642
and she descended into darkness

07:45.666 --> 07:47.276
and she was diagnosed

07:47.300 --> 07:50.571
with what we call
postpartum depression.

08:05.118 --> 08:07.588
Bless you my child.

08:09.022 --> 08:11.191
Maria is a high priestess.

08:14.962 --> 08:18.742
What do you do with
someone like Raymond?

08:18.766 --> 08:20.810
What would you like me to do?

08:20.834 --> 08:23.203
Well, he frightens me.

08:24.337 --> 08:26.239
So he should be locked up
because you're afraid?

08:36.616 --> 08:38.719
He's banishing your demons.

08:41.020 --> 08:43.131
