lecture actually.

09:42.049 --> 09:43.893
Will you be coming to any
more of my lectures?

09:43.917 --> 09:45.394
Erm, I, I don't know.

09:45.418 --> 09:48.932
I, I was so impressed
by, by what you said.

09:48.956 --> 09:53.803
