of psychology at Columbia.

09:53.827 --> 09:55.371
- Mm hmm.
- In New York.

09:55.395 --> 09:57.841
I know where it is, yeah.

09:57.865 --> 09:59.843
Of course you do,
it's in New York.

09:59.867 --> 10:01.845
