because the atom bomb

12:49.236 --> 12:50.337
was inside her.

12:51.571 --> 12:53.883
That is a delusion.

12:53.907 --> 12:56.552
The statesmen of the world
who boast and threaten

12:56.576 --> 12:59.956
that they have doomsday weapons
are far more dangerous

12:59.980 --> 13:03.492
and far more estranged from
reality than many of the people

13:03.516 --> 13:06.920
on whom they label
psychotic is affixed.

13:08.088 --> 13:09.990
Not wrong though am I?

13:11.992 --> 13:15.471
Normal fucking man has
killed 100 million

13:15.495 --> 13:19.166
of his fellow normal man
in the last 50 years.

13:21.301 --> 13:23.370
Whatever happened to her?

13:25.038 --> 13:26.249
Long time ago.

13:26.273 --> 13:29.085
I don't know, she
might still be there.

13:29.109 --> 13:31.420
Couldn't she come here?

13:31.444 --> 13:33.513
I mean, maybe she could
get some help here?

13:35.916 --> 13:37.460
Hang around, you'll find out.

13:37.484 --> 13:39.428
Oh I bet you say that
to all the girls.

13:39.452 --> 13:40.587
Aye, I do.

13:43.090 --> 13:45.568
Sorry, I'm already late.

13:45.592 --> 13:47.270
Patient?

13:47.294 --> 13:50.130
No, my kids are
down from Glasgow.

13:53.300 --> 13:54.878
Children?

13:54.902 --> 13:57.881
I didn't, I didn't realize
you were married.

13:57.905 --> 13:59.139
You didn't ask.

14:01.608 --> 14:03.352
So your wife...

14:03.376 --> 14:06.923
If it makes you feel any
better we're gettin' divorced.

14:06.947 --> 14:08.015
