14:22.429 --> 14:24.073
or even like each other anymore.

14:24.097 --> 14:25.574
And the children?

14:25.598 --> 14:29.202
Do you, do you not love or
even like them anymore?

14:30.303 --> 14:32.381
I love my children.

14:32.405 --> 14:34.942
If you loved them you'd stay.

14:36.176 --> 14:38.454
What the fuck do you know?

14:38.478 --> 14:40.957
I've read about the effects
of divorce on children.

14:40.981 --> 14:42.926
Well then you'll
know that growing up

14:42.950 --> 14:46.653
in a so-called fucking happy
family can destroy some people.

14:48.188 --> 14:50.433
I've seen what families
do to each other

14:50.457 --> 14:52.217
and I'm not puttin' my
children through that.

14:52.241 --> 14:53.302
A coward walks away.

14:53.326 --> 14:55.595
No, a brave man walks away.

14:59.432 --> 15:00.467
I'm sorry.

15:52.119 --> 15:54.721
No!

16:25.585 --> 16:29.732
Mrs. Holding, I, I know
it looks dreadful,

16:29.756 --> 16:31.600
but let me assure you.

16:31.624 --> 16:33.702
You can't even tell
me how it works.

16:33.726 --> 16:34.726
No.

16:36.396 --> 16:39.242
No, you're right, I can't.

16:39.266 --> 16:43.203
That's because we don't
know exactly why it works.

16:46.073 --> 16:48.384
But believe me, it does work.

16:48.408 --> 16:52.345
And it will work for John,
if he's allowed to stay.

16:56.149 --> 16:59.062
Well, think of it a little

16:59.086 --> 17:02.631
like mending a broken
radio by giving it

17:02.655 --> 17:05.134
a firm slap on the hand.

17:05.157 --> 17:06.835
But Johns not a radio.

17:06.858 --> 17:08.461
He's my son.

17:09.296 --> 17:12.265
It hurts him, and
he isn't better.

17:16.636 --> 17:18.446
What are you thinking?

17:18.471 --> 17:21.117
A visit to a mental institution,

17:21.141 --> 17:24.487
book signing, you know,
that kinda thing.

17:24.511 --> 17:26.289
What a week, two weeks, what?

17:26.313 --> 17:27.723
Yeah something like that.

17:27.747 --> 17:29.525
- Is that okay?
- Yeah.

17:29.549 --> 17:31.760
You know, radio, TV.

17:31.784 --> 17:33.829
I'm going to have to call
you back about all this.

17:33.853 --> 17:35.564
- Oh, okay.
- Yeah.

17:35.588 --> 17:37.100
Yeah, if you could call
me back, that'd be great.

17:37.124 --> 17:37.800
Yeah, we'll speak soon,
we'll speak soon.

17:37.824 --> 17:38.801
Okay, cool.

17:38.825 --> 17:41.137
- Okay, bye.
- Bye bye.

17:41.161 --> 17:43.239
So I was thinking I could

17:43.263 --> 17:47.243
