it to be more homey?

17:56.909 --> 17:59.379
I have to forgive you first.

18:00.447 --> 18:01.481
That's true.

18:08.921 --> 18:09.921
Oh, I see.

18:11.224 --> 18:13.236
I don't want you
moving anything.

18:13.260 --> 18:14.703
