18:14.727 --> 18:16.439
I won't touch a thing.

18:16.463 --> 18:19.142
Everything is in a
very particular place.

18:19.166 --> 18:20.343
Is it?

18:20.367 --> 18:22.778
You'll note my
filing system here.

18:22.802 --> 18:23.802
It's very...

18:24.837 --> 18:26.182
It's very unique.

18:26.206 --> 18:27.740
Worked out to a micron.

18:36.683 --> 18:37.683
Raymond.

18:39.186 --> 18:40.420
Raymond, Raymond.

18:42.322 --> 18:44.333
Follow your breathing,

18:44.357 --> 18:46.359
follow your breath, yeah?

