That's it.

18:53.466 --> 18:54.466
That's it.

19:35.408 --> 19:36.852
Mr. And Mrs. Holding.

19:36.876 --> 19:38.254
John?

19:38.278 --> 19:40.413
Do you want to come through?

19:45.952 --> 19:47.220
Hello, Raymond.

19:53.560 --> 19:54.560
This way.

20:06.773 --> 20:07.773
John.

20:13.813 --> 20:15.848
Mr. and Mrs. Holding.

20:18.017 --> 20:19.895
I'm Dr. Laing.

20:19.919 --> 20:23.256
I believe you've already met Dr.
Zemmell.

20:24.591 --> 20:25.925
He hears voices.

20:28.361 --> 20:31.664
Or at least we think he does.

20:38.004 --> 20:40.983
I think Dr. Meredith
means well but I...

20:41.007 --> 20:42.709
So why are we here?

20:50.917 --> 20:52.385
I'll be honest.

20:53.886 --> 20:57.590
I have great concerns
about leaving John here.

20:59.326 --> 21:03.763
We saw somebody eating
what looked like cat food.

21:05.031 --> 21:07.743
Some people say

21:07.767 --> 21:09.602
you are experimenting
on your patients.

21:10.903 --> 21:16.309
But I want John to be safe,
not in a mental hospital.

21:23.350 --> 21:25.785
I know I can't help him at home.

21:30.690 --> 21:32.000
According to Dr. Meredith,

21:32.024 --> 21:34.694
you're a catatonic
schizophrenic.

21:39.799 --> 21:42.978
John, could you at least
tell me what you want?

21:43.002 --> 21:45.013
I want my own room.

21:45.037 --> 21:47.640
